title: NATO WARPLANES STRIKE TRIPOLI, LIBYA
content: NATO warplanes hammered Tripoli on Tuesday with some of their heaviest air strikes yet after the United States said Libyan Leader Muammar Gaddafi would “inevitably” be forced from power, Reuters reported. nato_attackAt least twelve (12) huge explosions rocked the capital in the early hours.
